  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to investigate the effectiveness of a one-to-one, adult-to-youth primary
      preventive mentoring program in Sweden. Outcome domains and criteria for inclusion and
      exclusion of study participants are elaborated in collaboration with the providing NGO, and
      the program is given as customary.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
